To build and run

1. Install Go per http://golang.org/doc/install.html
2. go get github.com/araddon/httpstream
3. cd birdpinger
4. go build
5. ./birdpinger \
    --twitter_username=[username] \
    --twitter_password=[password] \
    --stream_spigot_hostname=<localhost:8081 or wherever streamspigot is running> \
    --stream_spigot_secret=<contents of app/birdfeeder/handlers/pingersecret.py`
